    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but honestly i just want to know if there's anything i can do myself for now to help with the breathing? like can i just take an extra puff of my albuterol inhaler when i feel this way or maybe try a supplement to help my lungs? i really'd rather avoid the clinic if i can just manage it at home.",
